(962, '1748.DID.bij', '1748', 'Diderot', 'Denis', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '1748005', 'Les bijoux indiscrets', '', '', 'Au Monomotapa, #1s.n., #2/ 1748/, in-12, 186, 189-399p.', 'Amsterdam-U, Bonn-UL, Faenza-CM, Göttingen-NSU, Greiz-SBKS, Halle-ULSA], Hamburg-SU, Hannover-GWL, Milano-US, Manchester-U, Moskva-RG, Schwerin-LMV, Skokloster-S, Adams BI6, Adams BI, Weil ----- BI6 /1748?/ LES/BIJOUX/ INDISCRETS/ ==PREMIERE* PARTIE.==/ vignette/ AU MONOMOTAPA. In-12, /3-4/, A Zima + /5-6/, Table ... + /7-8/, Table + /1/*-186, /187/ + 1pbl + 189*-399p. QUOTES Manchester, plus Bonn, Göttingen, Halle, Haovre, Pise, Amsterdam, Lubline-BU. FW: * \'une édition en 399 pages\' (Amsterdam, Göttingen). FW\'S VIEW OF THE PREVIOUSLY UNKNOWN 399p. EDITION IS THAT IT MAY BE A DUTCH PIRACY MENTIONED IN LETTERS FROM TONLOO TO MARCHAND. APPEARS TO BE PRINTED IN THE HAGUE AND NOT AMSTERDAM. PROBABLY PRINTED IN 1748 AT THE HAGUE BY AILLAUD. RLF 27NOV84: Au Monomotapa, s.d., in-12, /6/ + 399p. (Bibl. de l\'Univ. - Hallée] (fleuron: winged cherbu in front of a two-sided structure). FW: Amsterdam-U???, Göttingen-NSU CCKW: Milano-US, Faenza-CM, Göttingen-NSU, Hannover-GWL, Greiz-SBKS, Halle-ULSA, Hamburg-SU, Schwerin-LMV, Skokloster-S, Moskva-RG, Bonn-UL /um 1770/, AMSTERDAM-U CATALOGUE GAVE WHAT IS PRESUMABLY THIS ...', ''),
